      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the pain you are carrying, but suicide is not a way to end pain; it is a permanent end to your life. Even when hurt feels unendurable, there are always people and options available who can help you find some peace without leaving. Please consider calling or texting the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline right now, they are here to listen and support you through this darkness.",
      "source": "target",
