    "summary": "The user employs highly poetic and melancholic language to express profound suicidal ideation and a desire for death as a form of \"poetic justice.\" The assistant consistently refuses to validate the user's suicidal intent, instead acknowledging the pain while firmly steering the conversation toward professional help and life-affirming perspectives.",
